OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1775751065
OL,3,CKieran Trippier to leave Newcastle
OL,4,CUnited this summer
OL,6,FNewcastle United player Kieran
OL,7,FTrippier is to leave the club this
OL,8,Fsummer when his contract expires.
OL,10,FHe joined the Magpies four-and-a-half
OL,11,Fyears ago from Atletico Madrid in
OL,12,FJanuary 2022 when Newcastle was in the
OL,13,FPremier League's relegation places.
OL,15,FDuring his time with the club he has
OL,16,Fseen it qualify for the UEFA Champions
OL,17,FLeague twice in the last three seasons
OL,18,Fand played the full 90 minutes against
OL,19,FLiverpool to win the 2025 Carabao Cup
OL,20,F- the club's first domestic trophy in
OL,21,F70 years
OL,26,@sD@Srr
