OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1775751065
OL,3,CKieran Trippier to leave Newcastle
OL,4,CUnited this summer
OL,6,FTrippier has so far made more than 150
OL,7,Fappearances for Newcastle United, and
OL,8,Fscoring four goals. He has alsoJracked-
OL,9,Fup 54 senior international caps for
OL,10,FEngland.
OL,12,FSpeaking about his time with NUFC
OL,13,FTrippier said: "The time has come to
OL,14,Fleave this amazing club after four-and-
OL,15,Fa-half years. This is where I have
OL,16,Ffelt most at home. It's emotional, and
OL,17,FI'm really going to miss it.
OL,26,@uD@POU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
