OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1775751065
OL,3,CKieran Trippier to leave Newcastle
OL,4,CUnited this summer
OL,6,F"I want to say a massive thank you to
OL,7,Fthe supporters for all the support
OL,8,Fthrough the goodJand the bad times for
OL,9,Fme personally. You've always supported
OL,10,Fme, always stood by me.
OL,12,F"To my teammates, it's going to be
OL,13,Femotional. It's been an amazing
OL,14,Fjourney with you guys. I'm going to
OL,15,Fmiss you all, but to win a trophy with
OL,16,Fyou guys was really, really special -
OL,17,Fthe best of my career.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1775751065
OL,3,CKieran Trippier to leave Newcastle
OL,4,CUnited this summer
OL,6,F"And to the manager, Eddie Howe, all
OL,7,Fthe coaching staff and the team behind
OL,8,Fthe scenes, a massive thank you. The
OL,9,Fgaffer had the trust - twice - to sign
OL,10,Fme, gave me the opportunity to
OL,11,Frepresent and captain this great club
OL,12,Fand most importantly, we managed to
OL,13,Fwin a trophy.
OL,15,F"I'm going to miss everyone at the
OL,16,Fclub. Thank you."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOUxD@QO]
