OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1775751065
OL,3,CKieran Trippier to leave Newcastle
OL,4,CUnited this summer
OL,6,FHead Coach Eddie Howe commented:
OL,7,F"Kieran has been magnificent for us on
OL,8,Fand off the pitch. From the moment he
OL,9,Fwalked through the door, he has helped
OL,10,Fto drive standards that have changed
OL,11,Fthe club's trajectory.
OL,13,F"His performances on the pitch have
OL,14,Fbeen to the highest level. Building
OL,15,Fstrong partnerships with the players
OL,16,Faround him. His outstanding technical
OL,17,Fability helped elevate the team and
OL,18,Fhis strong crossing ability helped
OL,19,Fcreate many goals and chances for his
OL,20,Fteammates.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1775751065
OL,3,CKieran Trippier to leave Newcastle
OL,4,CUnited this summer
OL,6,F"His leadership skills have been
OL,7,Finvaluable. In difficult moments his
OL,8,Fexperience has proved calming and his
OL,9,Fdrive and will to win has inspired the
OL,10,Fplayers to keep pushing forward.
OL,12,F"While we'll be saying goodbye to
OL,13,FKieran shortly, we also know we have a
OL,14,Flot left to play for this season, and
OL,15,FI know a player of Kieran's character
OL,16,Fwill be giving absolutely everything
OL,17,Fto end his time here on a high."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/9
