OL,3,CKieran Trippier to leave Newcastle
OL,4,CUnited this summer
OL,6,FRoss Wilson, sporting director, at
OL,7,FNewcastle United's added: "Kieran
OL,8,Fshould be soJproud of the contribution
OL,9,Fhe has made to Newcastle United's
OL,10,Fprogress over the last four-and-a-half
OL,11,Fyears.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/9
