PN,42808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1775751065
OL,3,CKieran Trippier to leave Newcastle
OL,4,CUnited this summer
OL,6,F"I've admired Kieran from a distance
OL,7,Ffor many years, and seeing him up
OL,8,Fclose in recent months has only
OL,9,Freinforced the impact he has as a
OL,10,Fleader, both in the dressing room and
OL,11,Fon the pitch. When the time comes,
OL,12,FKieran will leave with the respect and
OL,13,Fgratitude of everyone connected with
OL,14,FNewcastle United. We wish him every
OL,15,Fsuccess in whatever comes next."
OL,17,FThe news comes ahead of the final
OL,18,Fseven matches of the current Premier
OL,19,FLeague season.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
